        <abstract>
            <p>Anticipated AG’s attitude on design in orchids. Does he not think that the variations that gave rise to fancy pigeon varieties were accidental?</p> 
<p>Has been working hard at <hi rend="italic">Lythrum</hi></p> 
            <p>and spontaneous movements of tendrils.</p> 
<p>Defends <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi> as a "sagacious animal" but does not know whether he will ever publish on it.</p> 
            <p>Comments on political situation in U. S.</p>
        </abstract>
